        public void run(int seed)
        The procedure of PSO
        • start timer
        • 1. initialize population
        • 2. initialize velocity
          • From generation = 1 to max generation {
          • Evaluate population
          • update Personal Best
          • Update Global best
          • Update Population
          • For Debug: Collect Global best Collect Particle
          • }
        • end timer
